      <title>汇丰银行受中东 IPO 浪潮推升 EMEA 排名榜首</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/hsbc-boosted-by-wave-of-middle-east-ipos-to-top-of-emea-ranking</link>
