      <title>加纳年度通胀率降至 19 个月低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/ghanaian-annual-inflation-rate-falls-to-19-month-low-of-26-4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[得益于与去年相比的基数效应以及央行积极收紧货币政策，加纳 11 月通胀率降至 19 个月低点。]]></description>
